[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302196_000014_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302196/8842_302196_000014_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "The task of the translator (and with all humility be it spoken) is one of some self denial.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "Thereafter, this sonnet bred in me desire to write down in verse four other things touching my condition, the which things it seemed to me that I had not yet made manifest.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "And I said these four things in a sonnet, which is this:--",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "But albeit I spake not to her again, yet it behoved me afterward to write of another matter, more noble than the foregoing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "And for that the occasion of what I then wrote may be found pleasant in the hearing, I will relate it as briefly as I may.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "Through the sore change in mine aspect, the secret of my heart was now understood of many.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "And as I was going that way by chance, (but I think rather by the will of fortune,) I heard one of them call unto me, and she that called was a lady of very sweet speech.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "And when I had come close up with them, and perceived that they had not among them mine excellent lady, I was reassured; and saluted them, asking of their pleasure.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000007_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000007_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "But when I still spake not, one of them, who before had been talking with another, addressed me by my name, saying, \"To what end lovest thou this lady, seeing that thou canst not support her presence?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "Then I, being almost put to shame because of her answer, went out from among them; and as I walked, I said within myself: \"Seeing that there is so much beatitude in those words which do praise my lady, wherefore hath my speech of her been different?\" And then I resolved that thenceforward I would choose for the theme of my writings only the praise of this most gracious being.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "Whereupon I declare that my tongue spake as though by its own impulse, and said, \"Ladies that have intelligence in love.\" These words I laid up in my mind with great gladness, conceiving to take them as my commencement.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000008_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000008_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "The poem begins here:--",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "The first part is a proem to the words following.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "The second is the matter treated of.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000014_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000014_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "The third is, as it were, a handmaid to the preceding words.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000014_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000014_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "The second begins here, \"An Angel;\" the third here, \"Dear Song, I know.\" The first part is divided into four.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000014_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000014_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "In the first, I say to whom I mean to speak of my lady, and wherefore I will so speak.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000014_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000014_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "In the third, I say what it is I purpose to speak so as not to be impeded by faintheartedness.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000014_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000014_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "The second begins here, \"And I declare;\" the third here, \"Wherefore I will not speak;\" the fourth here, \"With you alone.\" Then, when I say \"An Angel,\" I begin treating of this lady: and this part is divided into two.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000014_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000014_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "In the first, I tell what is understood of her in heaven.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000014_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000014_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "And that every vicious thought may be discarded herefrom, let the reader remember that it is above written that the greeting of this lady, which was an act of her mouth, was the goal of my desires, while I could receive it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302201_000014_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302201/8842_302201_000014_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "Then, when I say, \"Dear Song, I know,\" I add a stanza as it were handmaid to the others, wherein I say what I desire from this my poem.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302203_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302203/8842_302203_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "A few days after this, my body became afflicted with a painful infirmity, whereby I suffered bitter anguish for many days, which at last brought me unto such weakness that I could no longer move.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302203_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302203/8842_302203_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "And I remember that on the ninth day, being overcome with intolerable pain, a thought came into my mind concerning my lady: but when it had a little nourished this thought, my mind returned to its brooding over mine enfeebled body.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302203_000002_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302203/8842_302203_000002_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "She that was thine excellent lady hath been taken out of life.\" Then I began to weep very piteously; and not only in mine imagination, but with mine eyes, which were wet with tears.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302203_000002_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302203/8842_302203_000002_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "Then my heart that was so full of love said unto me: \"It is true that our lady lieth dead;\" and it seemed to me that I went to look upon the body wherein that blessed and most noble spirit had had its abiding place.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302203_000002_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302203/8842_302203_000002_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "Wherefore come now unto me who do greatly desire thee: seest thou not that I wear thy colour already?\" And when I had seen all those offices performed that are fitting to be done unto the dead, it seemed to me that I went back unto mine own chamber, and looked up towards Heaven.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302203_000002_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302203/8842_302203_000002_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "And so strong was my phantasy, that I wept again in very truth, and said with my true voice: \"O excellent soul! how blessed is he that now looketh upon thee!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302203_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302203/8842_302203_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "And as I said these words, with a painful anguish of sobbing and another prayer unto Death, a young and gentle lady, who had been standing beside me where I lay, conceiving that I wept and cried out because of the pain of mine infirmity, was taken with trembling and began to shed tears.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302203_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302203/8842_302203_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "Whereby other ladies, who were about the room, becoming aware of my discomfort by reason of the moan that she made, (who indeed was of my very near kindred,) led her away from where I was, and then set themselves to awaken me, thinking that I dreamed, and saying: \"Sleep no longer, and be not disquieted.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302203_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302203/8842_302203_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "Also, after I had recovered from my sickness, I bethought me to write these things in rhyme; deeming it a lovely thing to be known.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302203_000004_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302203/8842_302203_000004_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "Whereof I wrote this poem:--",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302203_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302203/8842_302203_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "\"And I became so humble in my grief, Seeing in her such deep humility, That I said: 'Death, I hold thee passing good Henceforth, and a most gentle sweet relief, Since my dear love has chosen to dwell with thee: Pity, not hate, is thine, well understood. Lo!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302203_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302203/8842_302203_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "I do so desire to see thy face That I am like as one who nears the tomb; My soul entreats thee, Come.' Then I departed, having made my moan; And when I was alone I said, and cast my eyes to the High Place: 'Blessed is he, fair soul, who meets thy glance!' ...",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8842_302203_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8842/302203/8842_302203_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8842",
        "content": "Just then you woke me, of your complaisaunce.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
